               <h2>LEGISLATIVE COUNSEL'S DIGEST</h2>
            </div><br /><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0"><span id="subject">SB2, Wiener
                  .
                  													Budget Act of 2024.</span></div>
            <div><span id="digesttext">
                  <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">The Budget Act of 2024 made appropriations for the support of state government for the 2024–25 fiscal year.</div>
                  <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">This bill would amend the Budget Act of 2024 by making changes to existing appropriations, as provided.</div>
                  <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;">This bill would declare that it is to take effect immediately as a Budget Bill.</div></span></div><span class="hidden">
